uk.ac.cam.cl.groupproject12.lima.hbase

Class Statistic

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.ac.cam.cl.groupproject12.lima.hadoop.AutoWritable
      • uk.ac.cam.cl.groupproject12.lima.hbase.Statistic
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

    public class Statistic
extends AutoWritable
    A class to represent a row in the HBase Statistic table, characterising the traffic through a router in a timeframe.
    Note: the totalDataSize is in bytes. Other fields are unitless.
